import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz';
import Button from '../lib/button';

const layoutProps = {
  
};
export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"button"}}>{`Button`}</MDXTag>

<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"variants"}}>{`Variants`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"default"}}>{`Default`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={0} __code={'<Button>Yay! I\'m a button</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
    <Button>
        Yay! I'm a button
    </Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"primary"}}>{`Primary`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={1} __code={'<Button primary>Yay! I\'m a primary button</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
    <Button
        primary
    >
        Yay! I'm a primary button
    </Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"destructive"}}>{`Destructive`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={2} __code={'<Button destructive>Destroy</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
    <Button
        destructive
    >
        Destroy
    </Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"full"}}>{`Full`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={3} __code={'<Button full>Full sized button</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
    <Button
        full
    >
        Full sized button
    </Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"small"}}>{`Small`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={4} __code={'<Button small>Small variant</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
    <Button
        small
    >
        Small variant
    </Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"large"}}>{`Large`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={5} __code={'<Button large>Large variant</Button>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Button}}>
    <Button
        large
    >
        Large variant
    </Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Button} />
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
